## Day 2: File and Directory Creation

## ğŸ“ 1. Creating and Deleting Files and Folders

| Task                   | Command                                 |
|------------------------|------------------------------------------|
| Create a file          | `touch filename.txt`                     |
| Create a folder        | `mkdir foldername`                       |
| Create nested folders  | `mkdir -p folder1/folder2/folder3`       |
| Delete a file          | `rm filename.txt`                        |
| Delete an empty folder | `rmdir foldername`                       |
| Delete a folder with files | `rm -r foldername/`                 |

> âš ï¸ Use `rm -i` to ask confirmation before deleting:  
> `rm -i important.txt`

